--Lets Know how to install packages.

Open Your Python Scripts File like you can explore in your local disk a Python Folder will be visible in Program Files Or APPData or Some Other.
Ex:   C:\Program Files\Python310\Scripts - This is Path if it is default Download 
Ex:   Python310\Scripts                  - Common Sub Path 
Open a Command Propmt at that location using right click then

pip install time
pip install pyautogui
pip install cv2

Additinol Packages :
pip install opencv-contrib-python==4.5.5.62

All Set -----!!!!
